headline: RenaissanceRe Q4 Earnings Beat on Premium Growth in Property Unit
summary: RNR's Q4 results benefit from account renewals as a result of the Validus buyout and higher yields from the fixed maturity portfolio, partly offset by an increase in claim expenses.
